long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A Leetcode Extension that helps in categorizing problems on the basis of Stars. Every problem in problemset is assigned some stars. A popular problem having good concept to learn and chances of problem to be asked in any interview is assigned with more number of stars. Likes of every problem are also given on the problemset page itself. Additionally problems can also be sorted on the basis of these categories.

The Extension allows you to choose problems wisely so that you can learn the most out of every chosen problem. Keep Coding ✌️
